RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT RATE_CODE, RATE_CODE_DESC FROM (SELECT DISTINCT A.RATE_CODE AS RATE_CODE, B.FIELD_DESC AS RATE_CODE_DESC, A.AUTH_STAT AS AUTH_STAT, A.RECORD_STAT AS RECORD_STAT FROM LFTMS_TREASURY_RATE_CODE A, OLTMS_STATIC_MAINTENANCE B WHERE A.RATE_CODE = B.FIELD_NAME AND B.MAINTENANCE_TYPE = 'RTCD' AND A.RATE_CODE_USAGE = B.FIELD_TYPE AND ? = 'T' UNION SELECT DISTINCT A.RATE_CODE AS RATE_CODE, A.RATE_DESCR AS RATE_CODE_DESC, A.AUTH_STAT AS AUTH_STAT, A.RECORD_STAT AS RECORD_STAT FROM CFTMS_RATE_CODE A, CFTMS_FLOAT_RATE_MASTER B WHERE A.RATE_CODE = B.RATE_CODE AND B.CCY_CODE = ? AND A.BRANCH_CODE = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND A.BRANCH_CODE = B.BRANCH_CODE AND ? = 'X' AND ? = 'U' AND sypks_utils.get_product(?) = 'D' UNION SELECT RATE_CODE, RATE_CODE_DESC, AUTH_STAT, RECORD_STAT FROM LFTMS_STANDARD_RATE_CODE WHERE RATE_TYPE = 'S') WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' ORDER BY RATE_CODE

SELECT DISTINCT RATE_CODE, RATE_DESCR FROM CFTMS_RATE_CODE WHERE BRANCH_CODE = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' UNION SELECT DISTINCT RATE_CODE, RATE_DESCR FROM CFTMS_RFR_MASTER WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND TYPE = NVL(?,TYPE)
SELECT RATE_CODE,RATE_CODE_DESC FROM LFTMS_STANDARD_RATE_CODE WHERE RATE_TYPE='P' AND RECORD_STAT='O' AND AUTH_STAT='A' ORDER BY RATE_CODE
